properties.query:
SELECT 
"Transaction_ID" as "order_id", 
"Transaction_Date" as "date",
"Purchase_Amount" as "payment",
"Product_Category" as "category",
"Country" as "country",
"country_code" as "country_code"
FROM FLOWFILE

properties.query:
SELECT 
"order_id" || '-' || "order_item_id" as "order_id", 
SUBSTRING("shipping_limit_date", 1, 10) as "date",
"price" * 5.64 as "payment",
"category",
"country",
"country_code"
FROM FLOWFILE
WHERE "order_status" = 'delivered' 
OR "order_status" = 'shipped'
